## Auto-Fail (< 98 regardless of score math)

- Design "improved" vs mockup
- Hardcoded colors outside tokens
- No isolated Preview tested
- Success reported without screenshot evidence

## Never

- **Never** skip review because Figma MCP was used
- **Never** accept "close enough" at 95
- **Never** proceed to next region at score < 98
- **Never** do more than 3 correction rounds without involving user

